e, stampedes in bread lines in London, infanticide, and even cannibalism throughout Europe.","jurisdictionLevel":2},{"id":1705192,"age":14,"year":"1328","julianDay":2206102,"title":"First War of Scottish Independence","description":"The First War of Scottish Independence began after England invaded Scotland in 1296. The Treaty of Edinburgh was signed in 1328 which declared peace between the two kingdoms and brought the war to an end.","jurisdictionLevel":2},{"id":1705193,"age":23,"year":"1337","toYear":"1453","julianDay":2209390,"title":"The Hundred Years' War","description":"The Hundred Years' War between France and England was largely due to the question of legitimate succession to the French crown.","jurisdictionLevel":2}],"lifeSummary":"Thomas Everard was born in 1314, in Leverington, Cambridgeshire, England. He had at least 1 son. He died in 1365, in his hometown, at the age of 51."},"et":{"1314–1365":"1314–1365","1340–1390":"1340–1390","1337":"1337","1315":"1315","1314":"1314","1365":"1365","1453":"1453","1340":"1340","1390":"1390","1328":"1328","1317":"1317","Leverington, Cambridgeshire, England":"Leverington, Cambridgeshire, England"},"fi":{"1314–1365":"1314–1365","1340–1390":"1340–1390","1337":"1337","1315":"1315","1314":"1314","1365":"1365","1453":"1453","1340":"1340","1390":"1390","1328":"1328","1317":"1317","Leverington, Cambridgeshire, England":"Leverington, Cambridgeshire, England"},"fr":{"1314–1365":"1314–1365","1340–1390":"1340–1390","1337":"1337","1315":"1315","1314":"1314","1365":"1365","1453":"1453","1340":"1340","1390":"1390","1328":"1328","1317":"1317","Leverington, Cambridgeshire, England":"Leverington, Cambridgeshire, Angleterre","lifeSummary":"Thomas Everard est né en 1314, à Leverington, Cambridgeshire, Angleterre. Il a eu au moins 1 fils. Il est décédé en 1365, dans sa ville natale, à l’âge de 51 ans."},"de":{"1314–1365":"1314–1365","1340–1390":"1340–1390","1337":"1337","1315":"1315","1314":"1314","1365":"1365","1453":"1453","1340":"1340","